name: web-design-cloner
description: Decompose concrete web references into reusable design signals without copying blindly. Use when the user shares a site, screenshot, landing page, dashboard, or says "quero nessa linha", "analisa esse layout", or "clona isso" as reference. Do not use for literal plagiarism, trademark copying, or when the task is already pure implementation inside an approved design system.
